+/*
+ * Lockless and Efficient Threaded Workqueue Abstraction
+ *
+ * Author:
+ *   Xiao Guangrong <xiaoguangrong@tencent.com>
+ *
+ * Copyright(C) 2018 Tencent Corporation.
